Package nl.tue.id.oocsi.client.behavior

Class OOCSIAwareness

java.lang.Object
nl.tue.id.oocsi.client.behavior.OOCSISystemCommunicator<java.lang.String>
nl.tue.id.oocsi.client.behavior.OOCSIAwareness
public class OOCSIAwareness
extends OOCSISystemCommunicator<java.lang.String>
OOCSIAwareness is a system-level primitive that allows for local representations of different OOCSI clients on the same channel and the data they share on that channel. The local representation will be about several keys or all data. This realizes synchronization on data without aggregation.
Author:
matsfunk
